                             SUPER NINTENDO
            GAME CHEATS, PASSWORDS & LEVEL CODES ( Dec 26, 1992 )

     The following list of Super Nintendo game cheats and level codes for
70 games was complied from an initial file by the Console Brotherhood and 
expanded by me by typing in magazine and Nintendo Player's Guide information.
Then before this file was released, a file on the Internet system maintained
by Robert Deloura appeared. I then incorporated some of his hints in my file.
I assume for the foreseeable future that these cheat files for both the SNES
and Sega Genesis will be a collaboration and other will contribute. 
	I expect that eventually as more games are released, the file will 
become a small book. Already it is 2790 lines (@ 66 lines per page = 42 pgs).
I've listed below the magazines that were used for this file so that readers
with other issues or missing magazines can add to this file. Feel free to add
to this file, but if you do list your changes in the section below. And for 
those who are too lazy to type in the cheats, mail Xerox's of magazine cheats
(Genesis pages too for a similar cheat file) to the address listed below. 
I will type them in.
     One final note. Sometimes you will see a set of passwords that doesn't
work on your version of the game. Remember that in many cases there is a
Japanese version of the game. Since I didn't start this file, it is quite
possible that some of the hints in this file are not for the USA version.
Also since I don't own most of these games, I haven't verified these cheats.

     Venice Postcard Co.  3710 Pacific Ave. #16  Venice, Ca, 90291 (USA)
