ACTRAISER
=========
Special Mode - To play only the action scenes all you have to do is finish
the game once and then if you move the cursor down at the title screen the
words SPECIAL MODE will appear.  Hit START and you will be able to play
thru only the action scenes without going into the creation mode.

Professional Mode - After completing the game, and your back on the title
screen, pressUp (or Down twice).  The "Professional" selection will appear 
below "New Game". You don't get any magic, and regular monsters take twice
as many hits to kill.

Hidden 1-Ups - There are 1-Ups hidden in the area of Bloodpool and Kasandora.
You can make them surface by controlling the elements. Create a rain shower
in the woods that are located northeast of the lake in Bloodpool. After the
storm, the villagers will uncover an artifact which they will offer to you.
This Source of Life will work as a 1-Up, giving you an extra chance to fight
off the forces of evil. You'll also dig up a Source of Life in Kasandora.
Once you've washed away the sand in the north and uncovered a pyramid, create
an earthquake. The walls of the pyramid will collapse and reveal this life-
giving treasure. The third one is collected by striking the Northwood temple
with lightning.

ADDAMS FAMILY
=============
Passwords - These passwords take you inside the Addams' mansion to help
find the missing family.

Start with only Morticia missing - BLKX8
   You will begin with everyone saved but Morticia. You'll also have five
   full hearts and 72 men. Begin the Trek in the Music Room. When Lurch
   finishes playing piano, the blocks around the door disappear and you will
   be able to enter the basement.

Start with Pugsley free - BZYXC
   You begin with Pugsley free and five hearts. Granny is the next family
   member in line for rescue, so start your search in the kitchen.

Start with Granny rescued - BDSXY
   You'll begin with Granny rescued and 72 men. Begin your search for
   Fester in the Portrait Gallery.

When you get a password after saving a family member or earning a heart,
reset the game and collect replenished 1 -UPs. You can carry up to 99 men
in reserve.

Incredible Codes:

   B&1&B  - 5 hearts, 80 lives and Granny & Pugsley rescued.
   71117  - 100 lives, 3 hearts and a sword.
   W111W  - 100 lives, 4 hearts and a sword.
   21112  - 100 lives, 5 hearts and a sword.

Secret Sites - Stand in the lower left corner of the Hall of Stairs (you will
be past the last door to the left). Push UP and there will be a secret door
that lead's to Pugsley's Den. Go through the 2nd secret door and you will be
"Behind the Stairs."
More 1-Ups are in the bear's mouth in the Lower Gallery. Walk into the mouth
shown at the right.
In the Portrait Gallery there are three 1-Ups, a Heart and a Baseball hidden
out of sight. When you reach the Lower Gallery, you'll find a bear rug that,
unlike the others, doesn't produce small bears. If you crawl into the mouth
of the bear, you'll be able to collect these elusive items

1-Up Room - After you have lost all of your lives playing the game, you can
earn more lives by stepping into a hidden room. There are two doors on the
Game Over screen. Walk off the left edge of the screen before you open either
of them and you'll end up in a hidden area that contains four floating 1-Ups.
Collect these valuable items and return to the previous screen. Open the
Continue door and move on with four additional lives in reserve.

Snap Along - The classic Addams Family theme which opens the game has the
sound of snaping fingers. During the music you can trigger the finger snaps
by pressing the L and R Buttons.

ARCANA
======
Stage or Chapter Select - Enter the following code when the START/CONTINUE 
title screen appaears. Press down Select, Select, X, Y, Select, Select,
L, R, Select, Select, left, right, up. Then choose the chapter with the
following keys: A - Stage 2,  B - Stage 3,  X - Stage 4,  Y - Stage 5.

Sound Room - To enter the Sound Room, on the title screen, hold L,R and B
buttons then push start.


BART'S NIGHTMARE
================
Easy 1-Ups - Choose the yellow door to enter the Itchy & Scratchy level. Once
you're inside, go to the area where the lamp is shooting out light bulbs.
Grab the weapon next to the lamp and blow away some bulbs. The first few
bulbs destroyed will give you 1-Ups.


BIG RUN
=======
Option Mode  - There is a way to adjust the game play in this intense
driver.  To set the controller how you want it just press SELECT at the
title screen.


BO JACKSON BASEBALL
===================
All Bo Squad - An entire squad of Bo Jackson's can play on any of the teams
in the game when you enter an easy code. After you have choosen your squad,
a team roster will appear. At that time, press Left on your Control Pad and
the Select and B buttons all at the same time. Every player on your team will
be replaced by Bo. This will make your team extremely tough to beat since 
Bo's video batting average is 3.99 and his Earned Run Average (as a pitcher)
is 1.53. 

