Enter Any Door - Type in the code word _JOSHUA_, make sure that there is a 
space before and after the password. (word is centered). Then press the Start
button. When the game begins, you will be able to walk directly to any room 
in the house.

Extra Pies - To get your pie reserves replenished, press the L and R buttons 
simultanously. Ten more pies will apear in your inventory.


THE LEGEND OF MYSTICAL NINJA
============================
