MAGIC SWORD
===========
Secret Options Screen - Enter the options mode and press down on the control
pad to highlight the word EXIT. Then press and hold the L and Start buttons
on Controller II, and press the Controller I Start button. A second options
screen will appear, allowing you to change your character's vitality for
extra endurance and select the starting floor. You can choose up to the
highest floor that you've been on in the current playing session. So you can
choose a level that you have played before.


ON THE BALL
===========
Level Select - To choose any level in the game, except for the last one, just
enter QWNQP on the password screen. Once you do this, the title screen will
appear again, but it will have the round number in the middle of the screen.
Press Up or Down to change the round number from 1 to 99. After choosing the
round, press Start and the screen will fade into the level of your choice.

2nd & 3rd Plane - Don't think the game is over when you complete the levels
in the first plane. At the title screen, access the password screen and enter
MHWYR to access the second plane, or HCCWD to reach the third plane. Each
plane has different levels ranging from upside down mazes to stages where you
can move slightly in one direction towards your destination.

Change Gravity - You can change the gravity by entering this code on the
password screen:  ZLJPJ
Make the gravity atch any of the planets in the solar system.

Change the Ball - This crazy code will allow you to change the ball into a
variety of objects such as a rag doll, space man, alien, etc. Enter this
code on the password screen:  GFXJF
After you enter the code, a screen will appear that will allow you to choose
from a variety of objects. When you start the game, the ball will no longer
have the usual look.

Sound Test - On password screen type:  NRRRP

See All Time Records - On password screen type: ZNGGX
A time record screen will appear which scrolls through every stage and gives
you the best time for that specific stage.


PAPERBOY 2
==========
Start on Higher Level - To start this game on the "HARD WAY" go to the
route option on the player select screen and enter the code: 6479 by
pressing right on the control pad. When ghosts and paperboy eating mastiffs
spot you pedaling by, they will come into the street and pursue you. Take
them out with well thrown papers.
To start on the MIDWAY level, enter the code: 5738 on the player select
screen. The action is faster than on Easy Street and there are new 
distractions and dangers. Pay attention to the traffic at intersections and
keep in mind the locations of the Attack Houses with their cannons and
gargoyles. 


PILOT WINGS
===========
Level Codes:

   Level        Codes
     1          000000
     2          985206
     3          394391
     4          520771
   Heli-1st     108048
     5          400718
     6          773224
     7          165411
     8          760357
   Heli-2nd     882943

Bonus Stages - Get to the bonus stages by accomplishing special maneuvers
on the Rocketbelt and Parachute rounds.  Ignore the rings and other
objectives in these rounds and maneuver your character over the moving
platform in each level.  If you can land on this portion of the target
area, you will be taken to the bonus stage with a perfect rating of 100
points!  When you are using the Rocketbelt and get this bonus, you will
be transformed into a winged man!  While in this special mode, try to
jump onto the trampolines and hit the power P's before landing in the
middle of the target.  When you enter the bonus stage in the parachute
rounds, you transform into a penguin who must high dive into a multi-
point pool!  The waters are separated by ropes which each designate
different extra point values.

HINTS on Landing on Moving Platforms:

  To land on moving platform with the parachute (level one):
        Immediately rotate 90 degrees right when released (ignore rings).
        Hold position until 630-40 feet, at which time pull rip-cord and
        then pull a quick u-turn (180 degrees). At 225 feet, rotate 90
        degrees right and line up with the moving platform track. When you
        reach the track the platform should pass underneath you and then
        return underneath you (traveling the same direction as you) -- As
        soon as you see it flare and hold.

  To land in the water target with the hang-glider:
        Hit thermal and wait till the glider levels out. Push up (dive)
        and right, drop to 150 feet, pull up and line up with the target.
        Obtain level flight and flare repeatedly just before the shadow
        hits the bottom edge of the target (not much, you should be no 
        higher than 25 feet).

  To land on the moving platform with the rocket-pack:
        Practice using the low burner and holding at 10 feet. Then
        practice stabilizing your position after moving forward (tricky).
        Complete the course and stabilize yourself over the platform's path
        in a place where you can see it approaching (at a corner or end of
        the 'track'). Drop like a rock the moment the edge of the platform
        hits your shadow.


POPULOUS
========
Full Power - At any time Press A then B.  Now hold Left and Press Right and
Press A, B, X in that order and then hit SELECT. Go to the swamp icon. If
it hasn't turned red then you have FULL POWER!

Stage Select - In Conquest Mode, push the Pause Icon and move the cursor
over the map. Now press the L Button and hold it as you press A. Next,
press and hold the R button, then press and release the Y, B, X, A, and
Select Buttons. Let go of the R Button and go to the Armageddon Icon. Press
the A Button and if the Icon stays gray, go to the Game Set up, move to
Conquest and press the A Button. Select your world using X and B.

