PRINCE OF PERSIA
================
To Change the Music While Playing - start a normal game, hit the START button
and hold it down, while doing this, press SELECT. You will then be presented
with a menu with 10 different level song selections. Up to 33 tunes can be
selected by scrolling the cursor past the 10th selection. Use the joystick
to select the song you wish to hear and press A or B to start the song and
continue playing. This song test is kind of a pain, beacuse each time you
want to change songs, you have to do the same thing over again.

Level Codes -  1: BRNGBB9    11: 7F39R1B
               2: MRG5L2X    12: H9TZD8N
